headline.print_headline: Uruguay Downs Slovenia 2-0 in World Cup Warm-Up
headline.main: Uruguay Downs Slovenia 2-0 in World Cup Warm-Up

lead_paragraph: Goals by Edinson Cavani and Christian Stuani lifted Uruguay past Slovenia 2-0 in a World Cup warm-up game Wednesday night.
